games.comment: Roddy White (2 catches, 54 yards) and Atlanta's other receivers. Ryan didn't have to throw the ball because the Falcons had the lead the entire game. If you're a White owner, I wouldn't be too concerned; the Falcons won't be winning many blowouts this season.    As for Detroit's receivers,
Roddy White is well past his prime and might not be back next season.
